items.name: Orianna | The Witcher 3 : Wild Hunt
items.description:
Character Lora of Orianna from The Witcher 3 : Wild Hunt (Blood & Wine)

"Lie still, lie silent, utter no cries." -Orianna

A dutchess, a witcher and 3 vampires walk into a bar. -soul3142


This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International License.

If you want to, you can support me on Patreon or Buy me Coffee.

My Witcher LoRA Index - soul3142's Guide to the Witcher Universe. additionally you can check out some characters i've made from other games also.

Main Trigger Word - oriannaW3_soul3142 , check examples for other ones.

RECOMMENDATIONS :-

  1. Highres Fix - must, if you are getting blurry and ugly images

    My upscale method: txt2img 512x768 -> send to img2img -> controlnet tile upscale, tile diffusion 2x scale with 4xUltrasharp upscaler and tiled vae

  2. Weight: 0.6 - 0.8

  3. Clip Skip: 2

  4. Denoising - Don't go too high, it can alter a lot of details

  5. For better face's - you can use ADetailer

I use 0.7 weight, 25 steps, Euler a, Clip skip 2 in nearly all my examples with almost same, simple +ve/-ve prompts regardless of checkpoint for my own consistency purposes.

There are imperfections here & there, which i usually leave it in as is, (i never do any inpainting in examples), most of which like hands can be fixed with better prompting, negative embeddings while other like weapons are just bad majority of the time no matter the model as of today.

Some LoRA's are flexible with any clothing, some are not (usually character's with single costume) so keep these things in mind.

This is an unofficial fanmade LoRA, not intended for any commercial purpose and use. All characters and IP rights are owned by their respective creators and owners. I do not own rights to any of these characters.

items.name: Futura Breeze
items.description:
My rating vs expectation: 85%

(Low quality dataset. Likeness is OK despite dataset. Training method could be better.)

All TIs I make depict real adults. Please apply it with good judgement. If you're the model and want this removed reach out to me via link below. I welcome all criticisms and suggestions with curiosity. If you like my work, buy me a house:
https://ko-fi.com/futurafree

This TI was trained in sd1.5 base with 5 vectors, 22 images, 5000 steps, and 227 epochs. This was finetuned for epiCRealism evo3 and Realistic Vision V4.0, but may work on others.

TIPS:

  • MUST be the first word in the prompt for likeness and consistency.

    • Example: futurabreeze5000v5, portrait of a woman, long dress etc.

    • Not: Portrait of futurabreeze5000v5, etc.

    • Sample images were not done this way because I was an amateur.

  • Recommended strength:

    • (0.98-1.0)

  • Optional:

    • Positive: no makeup

    • Negative: (nose ring:1.5)

  • I use adetailer for all images, with mediapipe_face_full, blank pos and neg, 1024x1024, inpaint mask blur: 20, inpaint noise strength: 0.45.

  • Again, prompt in adetailer is left blank most of the time; (*exception*: if Loras/Lycoris is used and has significant impact on the appearance of the model's face, copy paste pos prompt without Loras/Lycoris into adetailer).

  • Upscaler I use: 4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.
